Part 5 et grande final du Movie-Reviews Explosion of DOOM!

Shadow Of Chinatown (1936)
Note IMDB  : 4.3/10

Synopsis : A madman sets out to destroy a group of Chinatown merchants.

Commentaire : Un autre film avec Bela Lugosi. Mais le film en tant que tel a l'air très ordinaire, voir même plate.


Star Odyssey (1979)
Note IMDB : 2.7/10

Synopsis : Earth is attacked by an intergalactic villain and his army of robotic androids.

Commentaire : Ce film la à l'air parfait pour les soirée en gang. Tellement mauvais que c'en est drole.


Terror At The Red Wolf Inn (1972)
Note IMDB : 4.6/10

Synopsis:  College student Regina comes back to her room from class one day to discover she's won a getaway vacation at the quiet Red Wolf Inn. Before she can even call her parents to let them know where she'll be, the lodge owners arrange her transport and she soon finds herself with two other young women as guests of a kindly old couple. The place is beautiful and the food is fantastic, but something just doesn't seem right. One of the guests has suddenly vanished, and the hosts are certainly reluctant to have anyone poking around the meat locker. Still, the barbecued ribs are delicious, so what's there to complain about?

Commentaire : Une comedie mélangé avec un film d'horreur et toute les reviews sont positifs À être vu en gang..


The Manster (1959)
Note IMDB : 4.6/10

Synopsis : An American reporter in Japan is sent to interview an eccentric Japanese scientist working on bizarre experiments in his mountain laboratory. When the doctor realizes that the hapless correspondent is the perfect subject for his next experiment, he drugs the unfortunate man and injects him with a serum that gradually transforms him into a hideous, two-headed monster.

Commentaire : C'esrt un classique du genre qui a influencé plusieurs films. Je sais pas si c'est assez divertissant pour être écouté en groupe, mais il a l'air d'être assez bon pour étre écouté seul.


They (1974)
Note IMDB : 1.6/10

Synopsis : A group of young pilots in a remote region of the Canadian wilderness begin to hear strange reports over their radios about planes crashing, cars stalling and a deadly plague which has gripped the planet. It becomes clear that earth is in the midst of an invasion. The group of pilots decide to barracade themselves in a cabin deep in the woods and wait for their impending doom.

Commentaire : Plate plate plate. À jeter au poubelle.


This Is Not A Test (1962)
Note IMDB : 5.7/10

Synopsis : Late one night on a rural road in the western US, a policeman sets up a roadblock and begins stopping all traffic. When several cars and a big truck have stopped, he tells everyone why: a nuclear attack on the US appears to be underway, and since they have the truck there, their best chance at survival is to use it as a bomb shelter. Time is short and tensions in the small group quickly rise.

Commentaire : Un autre bon film, mais la non plus je croit pas qu'il soit fait pour être écouté en gang.


UFO: Target Earth (1974)
Note IMDB : 2.4/10

Synopsis : An electronics expert searching for evidence of aliens picks up signals that he believes are from an alien spacecraft--and they are coming from a lake near town.

Commentaire : Film plate à mort. avec rien d'interessant. Au poubelle.


Unkown World (1951)
Note IMDB : 4.0/10

Synopsis : Scientists use a gigantic drilling machine for an expedition to the center of the earth.

Commentaire : Le film a des reviews correct, mais de ce que je lit, il a pas l'air super le fun a regarder. Un gros bof


Warriors Of The Wasteland (1982)
Note IMDB : 4.2/10

Synopsis : Two mercenaries help wandering caravans fight off an evil and aimless band of white-clad bikers after the nuclear holocaust.

Commentaire : Une copie cheap du classique Mad Max qui a l'air super cheesy et ridicule. Le film parfait pour écouter en groupe.


Werewolf Woman (1976)
Note IMDB : 4.7/10

Synopsis : A woman has dreams that she is a werewolf so she goes out and finds men. She proceeds to have sex with them and then rip their throats out with her teeth. She eventually falls in love but then she is raped and her lover is murdered so she goes out for revenge.

Commentaire : Film que Mélanie adorerait j'en suis sur.

Movies reviews extravaganza PART FOUR4R4!

The Nightmare Never Ends (1980)
Note IMDB : 3.8/10

Synopsis : Police detective, Mitchell, investigating the death of a victim of a Nazi concentration camp discovers a nightclubbing playboy who has strange powers over women and is seemingly ageless.

Commentaire : Les commentaires disent toute que le film est pas très bon, mais qu'il est aussi très étrange et creepy. Pourrait être écoutable en gang j'imagine.


Panic (1976)
Note IMDB : 3.0/10

Synopsis : A scientist's experiment with a deadly bacteria goes awry and leaves him horribly deformed. The monstrous man then runs amok in his town

Commentaire : C'est pas mal unanime,  le film est plate, sans aucun budget et offre absolument rien d'interessant. À oublier.


The Phantom Creeps (1939)
Note IMDB : 4.4/10

Synopsis : A military intelligence officer and a pretty reporter try to find a scientist whose inventions can destroy the world.

Commentaire : Le film met en vedette le légendaire Bela Lugosi où il joue un scientifique fou qui essait de dominer le monde, ca l'air pas mal le fun comme film.


Piranha Piranha (1972)
Note IMDB : 3.2/10

Synopsis : Two wildlife photographers are traveling through the Amazon River basin on their latest assignment. While trying to capture the wildlife of the area on film, our photographers cross paths with a game hunter, who is stalking the animals for another reason.

Commentaire : Le film est plate a mort et le titre est trompeur, ya pratiquement aucun piranha dedans.


Prisoners Of The Lost Universe (1983)
Note IMDB: 4.1/10

Synopsis : Three people are transported into a parallel universe. There they find that they must use modern technology, but medieval weapons, in order to save the citizenry from a murderous warlord.

Commentaire : Petit budget mais semble être divertissant. Pourrait être un film a écouter en groupe


Purple Death From Outer Space (1966)
Note IMDB : 4.1/10

Synopsis : Edited version of the 1940 Universal serial "Flash Gordon Conquers the Universe", released in a syndication package to TV in 1966.

Commentaire : Je croit que c'est 6 épisodes d'une vielle émission de sci-fi classique. Comme y va manquer des gros boutte a l'histoire, je sais pas si ca vaut vraiment la peine de l'écouter.


Radio Ranch (1940)
Note IMDB : 5.9/10

Synopsis : Re-edited feature version of serial The Phantom Empire (1935). Singer Gene Autry discovers a race of advanced humans living beneath the earth.

Commentaire : Pas grand chose a dire sur celui la. Le film a l'air bizarre et divertissant j'imagine.


Ring of Terror (1962)
Note IMDB : 1.5/10

Synopsis : A group of medical students undertake some silly and frightening endeavors in order to pledge a fraternity

Commentaire : Ca l'air d'être incroyablement mauvais et il a aussi déjà passé à l'émission MST3K.


Robot Pilot (1941)
Note IMDB : 4.0/10

Synopsis : A test pilot and his weather observer develop a "robot" control so airplanes can be flown without pilots, but enemy agents get wind of it and try to steal it or destroy it.

Commentaire : Comedie romantique déguiser en drame d'espionnage. Semble pas être super interessant.


The Severed Arm (1973)
Note IMDB : 3.6/10

Synopsis : Trapped in a cave, five men cut the arm off of another companion in order to ward off starvation. After they are saved, their victim seeks revenge on them one by one.

Commentaire : Film d'horreur de serie-B très ordinaire. Encore un autre qui a pas l'air interessant.


De retour demain pour la grande final du Giga-Dance-Dance-Movie-Revolution Part 5!

Super-Mega-Plo-WOOOO MOVIES REVIEWS THE REVENGE part 3 oups caps.

House Of The Living Dead (1973)
Note IMDB : 2.8/10

Synopsis : A mad scientist (Mark Burns) is conducting hideous occult experiments at the family estate of Brattling Manor, monkeying about with things man was not meant to know, including the transfer and containment of living souls. It's only a matter of time before he begins to experiment on the souls of human beings - including his own family

Commentaire : L'histoire est bonne sauf que le film en tant que telle est plate. Mais apparament que la fin est pas mal cool. Je croit que je serait interessé a l'écouter.


How Awful About Alan (1970)
Note IMDB: 5.7/10

Synopsis: After a fire which killed his father and scarred his sister, a guilt-ridden victim of psychosomatic blindness is released from a mental hospital and goes back home to stay with his estranged sister. However, it appears that someone is out for revenge and wants to drive him crazy.

Commentaire : Je pense qu'on vient de trouver un gagnant! Toute les reviews sur IMDB sont super positifs et disent que, pour un Tv-made movie (équivalent des direct-to-dvd de nos jours), c'est un excellent thriller psychologique. Un autre que je voudrait bien écouter.


Idaho Transfer (1973)
Note IMDB : 5.3/10

Synopsis : A crew of young researchers escape into the future to avoid the shutdown of their project. They find that some type of 'eco-crisis' disaster has de-populated the area around their lab (in rural Idaho) and, by implication, the nation or maybe the world. Stranded in the barren future, in their travels they encounter an abandoned freight train possibly full of corpses (maybe, it isn't very clear). One of them travels further into the future and meets a family in a futuristic automobile, implying that that humankind has recovered from the disaster (or have they?)

Commentaire : L'histoire est vraiment vraiment cool et selon les reviews, c'est aussi un excellent film. Un autre que je veut voir!


The Lost City (1935)
Note IMDB : 5.6/10

Synopsis: An evil scientist plots to take over the world from his base in Africa, where he has invented a machine that can cause earthquakes.

Commentaire: Le film a l'air incroyablement divertissant. Les acteurs sont épouvantablement mauvais (ce qui est toujours drole), c'est super raciste (ce qui peut être très drole aussi) et a des décors impressionnant pour un petit budget. À écouter en gang.


The Lost City 2 (1935)
Note IMDB : 4.7/10

Synopsis : Second feature version of the 1935 serial of the same name, consisting of material from the first and last few episodes.

Commentaire : Je suis pas sur de comprendre exactement mais ca l'air d'être la suite de l'autre. À écouter en gang aussi.


The Lost World (1925)
Note IMDB : 7.1/10

Synopsis: The first film adaptation of Sir Arthur Conan Doyle's classic novel about a land where prehistoric creatures still roam.

Commentaire : Comme je disait l'autre fois, ce film la est un grand classique. C'est le premier film de monstres jamais fait et le premier a utiliser du stop-motion. Définitivement un film a écouter en gang.


Maciste In Hell (1925)
Note IMDB : 7.2/10

Synopsis : The devil takes Maciste down to hell in an attempt to corrupt and ruin his morality.

Commentaire : Un AUTRE très bon film! L'histoire est très cool et apparament que le film en tant que tel est époustouflant. Encore un autre a écouter en gang.


Menace From Outer Space (1956)
Note IMDB : 3.5/10

Synopsis : A two-part episode of the sci-fi TV series "Rocky Jones, Space Ranger"(1954), released as a feature.

Commentaire : C'est en fait 3 épisodes d'une vielle émission de sci-fi. Ca pas l'air très bon.


The Mistress Of Atlantis (1932)
Note IMDB : 5.8/10

Synopsis : Two French Foreign Legionnaires are lost amid the shifting sands of the Sarah Dessert when they stumble across the entrance to an underground world. Searching this new found subterranean passage, our heroes are surprised to find the lost city of Atlantis. Ruling over this fantastic underworld realm, an evil queen sets her sights upon these strangers to her kingdom.

Commentaire : Film très beau visuellement mais avec une histoire dure a suivre. Bof.


Night Fright (1967)
Note IMDB : 1.9/10

Synopsis : A government space experiment into the effects of cosmic rays on animal life goes horribly wrong, creating a mutant monster that terrorizes a rural community.

Commentaire : Film très très plate avec absolument rien de divertissant. À éviter.

Partie 4 demain soir sans faute. Tourlou.
